---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Pendle Forest Orienteers — orienteering across East Lancashire"
  description="A small orienteering club covering the moors, woodland and mill towns of East Lancashire. 12–15 events a year. Newcomers always welcome."
>

<main id="main">

  <!-- ─────────────────────────── HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-backdrop" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/assets/photos/training-moorland.jpg" alt="" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
    </div>
    <!-- faint topographic contour background, layered on top of the scrim -->
    <svg class="contour-bg" viewBox="0 0 1200 700" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
      <path d="M-50 140 C 180 80, 360 200, 540 150 S 900 80, 1250 170"/>
      <path d="M-50 220 C 220 170, 440 280, 660 230 S 1000 170, 1250 260"/>
      <path d="M-50 320 C 240 270, 460 380, 680 330 S 980 240, 1250 350"/>
      <path d="M-50 420 C 200 380, 420 480, 640 430 S 960 350, 1250 440"/>
      <path d="M-50 520 C 260 470, 480 580, 700 530 S 980 450, 1250 540"/>
      <path d="M-50 620 C 220 570, 440 680, 660 620 S 1000 540, 1250 630"/>
    </svg>

  <div class="hero-wrap">

    <div class="hero-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow rise d-2">East Lancashire · a British Orienteering club</p>
      <h1 class="rise d-3">Orienteering across the moors, woodland and mill towns of <em>East Lancashire</em>.</h1>
      <p class="lede rise d-4">A small club running twelve to fifteen events a year — midweek street-Os, weekend regionals on the fells, and training for members. Turn up, pick a course, and navigate your way round at your own pace. <a class="lede-link" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/info/membership">Join us →</a></p>
      <div class="hero-cta rise d-5">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/info/what-is-orienteering">Find your first event <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/events">All upcoming events</a>
      </div>
      <dl class="hero-stats rise d-6">
        <div><dt>Mapped areas</dt><dd>30+</dd></div>
        <div><dt>Covering</dt><dd>Burnley → Blackburn</dd></div>
      </dl>
    </div>

    <aside class="next-event rise d-4" aria-label="Next event">
      <p class="eyebrow">Next event</p>
      <p class="event-when">Wed 29 April · 7:00pm</p>
      <h2>Ightenhill South Urban</h2>
      <p class="event-where">Score event · Burnley · Local level</p>
      <p class="event-terms">
        <span>45 min</span>
        <span>From £6</span>
        <span>80 capacity</span>
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary btn-full" href="https://www.sientries.co.uk/event.php?event_id=17463" rel="noopener">Enter via SI Entries <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
    </aside>
  </div>
  </section>

  <!-- contour divider -->
  <div class="contour-divider" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1200 22" preserveAspectRatio="none" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
      <path d="M0 11 C 100 4, 220 18, 340 11 S 560 4, 700 11 S 920 18, 1060 11 S 1200 4, 1200 11"/>
    </svg>
    <span class="coord">53°48′N · 02°16′W</span>
  </div>

  <!-- ─────────────────────────── UPCOMING -->
  <section class="upcoming">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">Also coming up</p>
      <a class="sec-link" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/events">Full calendar →</a>
    </div>
    <ul class="event-row">
      <li>
        <a class="ev-card" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/events/oswaldtwistle-2026-05-06">
          <span class="arrow-mono">→</span>
          <time>Wed 6 May</time>
          <h3>Oswaldtwistle</h3>
          <p class="ev-sub">May Street-O</p>
          <span class="level level-local">Local</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="ev-card" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/events/brun-valley-regional-yb-2026-05-16">
          <span class="arrow-mono">→</span>
          <time>Sat 16 May</time>
          <h3>Brun Valley</h3>
          <p class="ev-sub">Regional &amp; YB · Burnley</p>
          <span class="level level-regional">Regional</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="ev-card" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/events/barrowford-2026-06-03">
          <span class="arrow-mono">→</span>
          <time>Wed 3 Jun</time>
          <h3>Barrowford</h3>
          <p class="ev-sub">Snook-O · June series</p>
          <span class="level level-local">Local</span>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="ev-card" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/events/blackburn-2026-06-10">
          <span class="arrow-mono">→</span>
          <time>Wed 10 Jun</time>
          <h3>Blackburn</h3>
          <p class="ev-sub">Snook-O · June series</p>
          <span class="level level-local">Local</span>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- ─────────────────────────── SOCIAL STRIP -->
  <section class="social-strip" aria-label="Follow us on social media">
    <div class="social-wrap">
      <div class="social-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Stay in touch</p>
        <h2>Event updates, photos, and last-minute changes.</h2>
        <p>Weather calls, course photos, and the post-race chat all live on our socials. Give us a follow so you don't miss the shout about tomorrow's event.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="social-buttons">
        <a class="social-btn" href="https://www.facebook.com/pendleorienteer/" rel="noopener" aria-label="Follow Pendle Forest Orienteers on Facebook">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M13 22v-8h3l1-4h-4V7.5c0-1.2.4-2 2-2h2V2h-3c-2.8 0-4.5 1.6-4.5 4.5V10H6v4h3.5v8H13z"/>
          </svg>
          <span>
            <strong>Follow on Facebook</strong>
            <span class="handle">@pendleorienteer</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <a class="social-btn" href="https://www.instagram.com/pendleforestorienteerers/" rel="noopener" aria-label="Follow Pendle Forest Orienteers on Instagram">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="4.5"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/>
            <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
          </svg>
          <span>
            <strong>Follow on Instagram</strong>
            <span class="handle">@pendleforestorienteerers</span>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─────────────────────────── WIDER SPORT (British Orienteering) -->
  <section class="wider-sport" aria-label="British Orienteering news">
    <div class="ws-grid">
      <div class="ws-brand">
        <a class="bo-logo" href="https://www.britishorienteering.org.uk/" rel="noopener" aria-label="British Orienteering">
          <img src="/assets/british-orienteering.svg" alt="British Orienteering">
        </a>
        <p>PFO is a member club of British Orienteering, the national governing body for the sport in the UK.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ws-feed">
        <p class="eyebrow">From the wider sport</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-04-14">14 Apr 2026</time>
            <h3><a href="https://www.britishorienteering.org.uk/news_archive/6783/british_orienteering_announces_date_for_annual_general_meeting_2026" rel="noopener">British Orienteering announces date for Annual General Meeting 2026</a></h3>
            <span class="read">Read →</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-04-07">7 Apr 2026</time>
            <h3><a href="https://www.britishorienteering.org.uk/news_archive/6775/british_middle_championships_2026_results" rel="noopener">British Middle Championships 2026 — Results</a></h3>
            <span class="read">Read →</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-03-28">28 Mar 2026</time>
            <h3><a href="https://www.britishorienteering.org.uk/news_archive/6778/jec_2026_gb_team_announcement" rel="noopener">JEC 2026: GB Team Announcement</a></h3>
            <span class="read">Read →</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <time datetime="2026-03-22">22 Mar 2026</time>
            <h3><a href="https://www.britishorienteering.org.uk/news_archive/6777/eyoc_2026_gb_team_announcement" rel="noopener">EYOC 2026: GB Team Announcement</a></h3>
            <span class="read">Read →</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="ws-footer"><a href="https://www.britishorienteering.org.uk/news_archive" rel="noopener">All BO news →</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─────────────────────────── LATEST + NEWCOMERS -->
  <section class="bottom-split">
    <article class="featured-news">
      <a class="news-image" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/news/pfo-success-in-europe" aria-label="PFO Success in Europe">
        <img src="/assets/photos/podium-cret-2025.jpg" alt="Kay and Emma on the CRET 2025 podium in Toledo, Spain">
        <p class="news-caption">City Race Euro Tour · Toledo, Nov 2025</p>
      </a>
      <div class="news-body">
        <p class="eyebrow">Latest news</p>
        <h2>Two PFO titles at the 2025 City Race Euro Tour.</h2>
        <p>Kay and Emma defended their category wins at the final round in Toledo, Spain — nine cobbled European cities, five results to count, both kept hold of the trophies they first won in 2024. Here's how the year went.</p>
        <a class="more" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/news/pfo-success-in-europe">Read the story →</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <aside class="newcomer-cta">
      <p class="eyebrow">Never tried this?</p>
      <h2>The sport of finding your way, <em>at your own pace</em>.</h2>
      <p>Orienteering is running — or walking — with a map and compass, navigating between checkpoints in a wood or a town. No special kit. No fitness minimum. Fastest round wins, but most people are just trying to beat their own time.</p>
      <a class="btn" href="https://www.pfo.org.uk/info/what-is-orienteering">How it works →</a>
    </aside>
  </section>

</main>

</Layout>
